Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:20.03,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}翻译：Rcat、saya；校对：小光头、saya；\N后期：zipwinmax；繁体化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:11.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:30.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.62,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:42.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:45.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:57.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:11.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:30.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:42.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:45.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:57.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这次比赛结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就退出剑道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改参加别的什么部团好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理部就不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能做蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然饭量不大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是蛋糕多少我都吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖上厚厚的奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一个大大的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好像做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第13话\N老师们和学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下来我要打手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我这个外行人都看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人  好强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接着请换打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还没有试过打别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来教你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我刚才那样打我的手部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍挥动的同时向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微从有效打击部位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏离了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你往前迈的是左脚  下次注意换右脚来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来就是光靠手指一下一下挥的话就会使重心前倾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意身体也要适当地向前推进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我都要下场练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们少一个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我又不是剑道部的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有经验就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说的那么清爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦  腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快  根本看不清她的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来请打我的腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我叫做小川芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学  我不打无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我多看看你的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多看看川添同学是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠酷毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小姑娘是川添道场的独生女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添道场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  已经是我们这里最强的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…包括我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉河老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用正座也没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看她  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好比我们学校的男生还快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正是我部作为秘密兵器的最终武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫川添珠姬是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添…珠姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  芽衣  换我换我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个打我打我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下一个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要  好吗好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要打手部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道里啊  如果被漂亮的击中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会有些兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这种气氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊  那么的灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却只觉得护具很重好像机器人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果我勤加练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放弃剑道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能达成那种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的女生都是上高中后才开始练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没人打得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  我能打包带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟  这可不行哟  客官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更像这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不对不对！我在认真个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个笨蛋！笨蛋真是个我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我是不是也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来让大家看一场自由对打吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看！想看！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生那边好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  从刚才开始就一直在拍小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山脚下欧姆叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜又一夜人见倾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:11.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}（日本的算术很多都是有口诀的，其中不仅有跟我们一样的乘法口诀，一些符号也有，\N小都此时念的「富士山(ふじさん)山麓(さんろく)にオーム鳴(な)く」是根号5的意思，\N「一夜(ひとよ)一夜(ひとよ)に人見頃(ひとみごろ)」是根号2的意思。）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都好帅哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个时候也很帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经那么帅气的小都竟然还开始练剑道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～受不了啦～人家最爱小都啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您现在拨打的电话正在停机中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请查询后再拨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  感觉大家都变得很有热情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  变得有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也让我上了一课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想要和她交手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引胴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就像遇到好事情时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深震撼着大脑的  那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强！好强！好强！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该更灵活…打得更好才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一局！拜托你再与我打一局！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我打一场吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一场吧…打一场吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BANBOO BANBOO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东她…是那么有气势的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的动作也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东她是仅限今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东～要是从小珠那里拿到一本你就太厉害了  太完美啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的学生都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我教得很随便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我当学生的时候可是要严格许多的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在要是这样  初学者也跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  确实我太过随便也是原因所在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师不是很热血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是最近以来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很久以前就在练剑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的学生们啊  练起剑道来好像总是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就跟当年的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  曾经非常地讨厌剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看清了  也能动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  只要等找回手感  身体就能自然地反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再打一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  谢谢  川添同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  暂停  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  为什么你这么强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来  先让经理安排一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是哪里的止汗剂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚出的哦  这边没得卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  你其实很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戴眼镜也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这是平光眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样会变得聪明点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都  开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都很怕的那个跟踪狂  不就是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面总是有些小鬼爱欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是被朋友欺负  是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林老师曾经是胆小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我这副样子  父亲硬是逼我去学剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我当然不想练什么剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算父亲已经买好了剑道用具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是很顽固  说什么也不肯去练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我看到了整套剑道用具的价格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对当时年幼的我  那可是笔天文数字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我家又很穷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我开始认真练起剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了不浪费那么昂贵的用具这种动机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是对了我的胃口  竟然不知不觉变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗  令尊也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实那些用具  是别人那里得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲戚的小孩学了一个星期就放弃了  所以转送给父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我知道实情的时候  已经不再想要放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道已经成了我身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是痛苦还是快乐  都包括在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是这样跟剑道相遇的  除了这个我什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能教得这么严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不也很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  又一个女生退部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的剑道用具  又该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像同样也有一个孩子决定要继续练下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为今天来了这里一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我  是因为小珠在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么说也很了不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…因为是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们室江剑道部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那些爱欺负人的家伙  现在也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时代在变  孩子们也在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始练剑道的理由  还有继续练下去的理由也会变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不会改变方针
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  剑道是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错  老师永远是林老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  往后我仍然会严厉地教下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再有吃不了苦练了一周就放弃的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一周  也一定会对他一生有所影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…林老师好帅～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  偶尔看到高兴的学生也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林老师好棒～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下  我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  接着就是正式比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要全力以赴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  对战顺序怎么排？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳来定？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…太乱来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你要不要试试先锋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  赶快打完回家也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是认真排的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次锋小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中坚是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副将纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样定就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将的话…不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将应该由部长担…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将啊  是由最强的人来担当的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是王的话  大将就是将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是女神的话  大将就是三大神器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拜托你了  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…一点都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就当先锋哦  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我一定尽力  全力以赴把大家的气势打出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  热血FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东同学一定做得到的  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能否回应大家的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦  我怎么被牵着鼻子走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东  开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  小东东  腹部得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说纪梨乃  你都算好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先让小东东重操剑道  逐渐回忆起乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她再也离不开这个世界对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到小东东这么单纯  计划竟然如此顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了  这个人竟然说了别人单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会不心潮澎湃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一年级生就大将…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次锋  上前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那简直要杀了人一般气势的小都真是太让人受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我还是不行的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…我们部很强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次  不能再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然比赛结束了  我们也来比一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林老师可是七段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢得了才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  这人居然这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你也得稍微像点大人样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部  至少也该拿到一胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来老师是真的很强…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:40.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小次郎老师  太丢脸了）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是场不错的比赛啊  小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:21:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点吧  她已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～实在是太帅了  小都～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小川芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由于比赛  肚子格外地饿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:24:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来就吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便  下集的竹剑少女是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小莉莉的决意和咀嚼的声音」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再来一份～
